.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
curl \-L http://bootstrap.saltstack.org | sudo sh \-s \-\- \-M \-N
.ft P
.fi
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.sp
The script should also make it simple to install a salt master, if desired.
.sp
Currently the install script has been tested to work on:
