If you have certificate issues using \fBcurl\fP, try the following:
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
curl \-\-insecure \-L http://bootstrap.saltstack.org | sudo sh \-s \-\- git develop
.ft P
.fi
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.sp
Using \fBwget\fP to install your distribution\(aqs stable packages:
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
