    <http://docs.saltstack.com/topics/conventions/formulas.html>\(ga_.

Available states
\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-

\(ga\(gafoo\(ga\(ga
    Install the \(ga\(gafoo\(ga\(ga package and enable the service.
