    {\(aq<package>\(aq: {\(aqnew\(aq: \(aq<new\-state>\(aq,
                   \(aqold\(aq: \(aq<old\-state>\(aq}
    },
    ...
}
.ft P
.fi
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.sp
CLI Example:
.INDENT 7.0
.INDENT 3.5
