.sp
.nf
.ft C
http://docs.aws.amazon.com/general/latest/gr/rande.html#s3_region
.ft P
.fi
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.sp
The service_url will form the basis for the final endpoint that is used to
query the service.
